Title: 049: Great Tips on Building a Successful Analytics Culture
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the President and Founder of Tiber Solutions Jim Hadley. You will be able to learn a different approach to hiring, get great tips and hacks on how to build an analytics culture, you will also hear about Star Schema and ETL, and be able to discover what a successful analytics workplace should look like.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/49
